## 📦 ROS2 Workspace Structure

```
ros2_ws/
└── src/
    ├── my_py_pkg/              # Python package
    ├── my_cpp_pkg/             # C++ package
    └── my_robot_interfaces/    # Custom interfaces
        ├── msg/
        │   ├── HardwareStatus.msg
        │   └── LedStateArray.msg
        └── srv/
            ├── ComputeRectangle.srv
            └── SetLed.srv
```
HOW TO CREATE AND BUILD CUSTOM INTERFACE
ros2 terminal command 
"
cd ros2_ws/src/
ls
ros2 pkg create my_robot_interfaces
ls
my_robot_interfaces
ls
rm -r include/ src
"
